---
title: New York Strip Steak with Truffle Butter over Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Asparagus
description: Ever tried truffle butter? It’s the stuff gourmet dreams are made of. Which means that this recipe is nothing short of a holy grail for any sophisticated foodie, because it’s also got a beautiful and tender New York strip steak for you to dollop all of that deliciousness on. Even the creamy potatoes, roasted asparagus, and demi-glace pan sauce that come with it seem to elevate things with their richness.
